resources.string: XML Umguquleli Free ayikwazanga bamisa internet udibaniso. Qiniseka uxhulumeneyo kwi umsebenzi womnatha kwaye uzame kwakhona.
* Nceda musa alter engundoqo XML ulawulo *
Khangela yakho Google Drive yakho iguqulelwe XML lwamagama!
Khetha ulwimi lwakho XML lwamagama kwaye khetha babuza iilwimi.
Vumela XML Umguquleli Free imvume ukufikelela kwi i-Google Drive-akhawunti yakho oyikhethileyo.
Ukuguqulela kwaye layisha phezulu .xml iifayili. Oku kungathatha okomzuzwana. Ndiyabulela kuba yakho umonde.

Kufuneka ufikelele okanye ingaba malunga ukufikelela yakho 3000 uphawu yonke imihla umda kuba free iinguqulelo. Ukuqhubeka ukuguqulela .xml, ukhuphele XML Umguquleli ku-20 dollazi inyanga kunye akukho ukucinywa imirhumo!
Nceda ukhethe ENYE ulwimi ukuguqulela ukusuka
Ngokusebenzisa le nkqubo, wena page imvume kwi-disclaimer kwaye uyavuma ukuba imiqathango yalo.

I-dala isiqulathi-zifayili kwesi sicelo akakwazi ukwenza nawuphi na iziqinisekiso malunga completeness, reliability kwaye uqukuqelo ye-generated data. Nayiphi na intshukumo uthatha phezu ulwazi ufuna ukufumana kule nkqubo ngu strictly e eyakho umngcipheko. I-dala isiqulathi-zifayili le nkqubo ayisayi kuba netyala kuba nayiphi na ilahleko kunye/okanye umonakalo othe kwi-unxulumano kunye sebenzisa le nkqubo.

I-dala isiqulathi-zifayili le nkqubo akubonakali\'t explicitly isibonelelo ukusebenzisa i-data intsalelo esi sicelo\'s iinkonzo. Kubalulekile ukuya kwi-umsebenzisi le nkqubo ukugqiba umda we allowable ukusetyenziswa data enikezwa kwesi sicelo\'s iinkonzo. Nangona kunjalo, ukusetyenziswa esi sicelo\'s iinkonzo ayisayi alter na copyrights okanye ukusetyenziswa neemvume enikezwa data.
Nceda ntaba kuyabhaleka wangaphandle yokugcina eendaba ukuze sebenzisa olu setyenziso.
Funda wangaphandle imvume kuyimfuneko ukufunda isicelo iifayili.
Bhala wangaphandle imvume eyimfuneko ukubhala isicelo iifayili.
